packages.name: physx
packages.description: The NVIDIA PhysX SDK is a scalable multi-platform physics solution supporting a wide range of devices, from smartphones to high-end multicore CPUs and GPUs. This is the latest NVIDIA official version of the PhysX engine which also directly integrates into Omniverse. This port is NOT officially supported by NVIDIA.
